*Izvinite* mi, zaboravio sam da vam platim račun. (I apologize, I forgot to pay the bill.)

Ne znam zašto, ali *izvinite* što nisam bio korektan prema vama. (I don't know why, but I apologize for not being polite to you.)

Molim vas *izvinite* što sam to rekao. (I'm sorry for saying that.)

*Izvinjavam* se, nisam znao da je to zabranjeno. (I apologize, I didn't know it was forbidden.)

*Izvinite* što vas ometam. (I apologize for interrupting you.)